replies.msg:
Laxalt's agent to @cmdotcom: &quot;The fans will see the real Laxalt next year. The player's intention is to remain at Milan. He firmly believes that he can impose himself on the club, but we also need to understand what the choice of the club and the new coach will be.&quot;<br />
<br />
Laxalt's agent: &quot;We will wait for the decisions of others, but we haven't made steps to find an alternative solution for Laxalt. Rumours also arrive here in South America; we only hear the news from the newspapers. For the moment, Torino or any other club haven't contacted us.&quot;

